docker-chromedriver
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Usage:

  $ docker run --net=host -t wakaba/docker-chromedriver:stable /cd
  $ docker run --net=host -t wakaba/docker-chromedriver:chromium /cd

... then access <http://localhost:9515/{path}>.

Docker Hub: <https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/wakaba/docker-chromedriver/>


ChromeDriver <https://sites.google.com/a/chromium.org/chromedriver/>
ChromeDriver <https://code.google.com/p/selenium/wiki/ChromeDriver>
The WebDriver Wire Protocol
<https://code.google.com/p/selenium/wiki/JsonWireProtocol>


Firefox: <https://github.com/wakaba/docker-firefoxdriver>